  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink40-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">ulakiyal paṟṟit talaivaṉ taṉ maṉaikkaṇ oru ñāṉṟu pōṉatē koṇṭu avvaḻip
          piriyātu uṟaikiṉṟāṉ eṉṟu ayaṟparattaiyar palarum kūṟiṉār eṉpatu kēṭṭa kātaṟparattai avar
          pāṅkāyiṉār kēṭpat taṉ tōḻikkuc colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink40">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> amma vāḻi tōḻi makiḻna</l>
          <l> ṉoṇṭoṭi muṉkai yāmaḻap pirintutaṉ</l>
          <l> peṇṭi rūriṟai koṇṭaṉa ṉeṉpa</l>
          <l> keṇṭai pāytara vaviḻnta</l>
          <l> vaṇṭupiṇi yāmpa ṉāṭukiḻa vōṉē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l> Alas, [my] friend! </l>
          <l> The bringer of delight</l>
          <l> has left [us], with bright bracelets on [our] forearms, to cry.</l>
            <l> They say has taken to tarrying in his wife's village.</l>
          <l>  [But he is] lord of the land of white lotuses</l>
            <l> with bees in [their] buds</l>
          <l> that open while keṇṭai fish leap uncontrollably towards them.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
